{"tid":31992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭周四知悉：變化巨大會重新考慮參選","createTime":"2016-12-10T03:19:55.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-10T03:28:53.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c76c92946811a8e1bd9e2c7a33c68c5f70b515de","tid":31992,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161210/large/1481339305_7b97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161210%2Flarge%2F1481339305_7b97.jpg&h=ff958609&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長林鄭月娥表示，在特首梁振英宣佈前一天即周四獲悉梁特棄連任一事，感到非常意外，對梁特保護家庭的決定表示理解尊重。她指4年多以來，與梁特是最緊密夥伴，指社會對他不太公道，由於現時變化非常巨大，自己不能不重新考慮情況，會好認真考慮參選，有決定時會講。<br />\n<br />\n她指考慮3個因素，是否有利落實高度自治港人治港、是否可按特首行之有道並求變去繼續施政、是否獲家人諒解。她稱知道今日之言會引來批評，會被指反口食言、以退為進，但今日眼前的問題不是個人名聲問題。不過，她強調此刻未為參選做一丁點準備。"},{"pid":"066c16276ac8f34eb367b8227888941296f569bf","tid":31992,"uid":62257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:20:38.000Z","msg":"燒山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51e222e2e009e73b5c29ba9a59a324b3517121a6","tid":31992,"uid":35094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:28:28.000Z","msg":"仆街啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38df26cc321fab6559fbd741d4cc92df2141422e","tid":31992,"uid":8810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-10T03:28:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://goo.gl/images/v1AcRb\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fimages%2Fv1AcRb&h=2ddada46&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}